Abraham Lincoln High School (ALHS) is a California Distinguished public high school located in the Sunset District of San Francisco, California. In 2017, ALHS was ranked #822 and earned a silver medal by U.S. News & World Report, placing it in the top 3% of public high schools nationally.
ALHS is a comprehensive high school with a long history of excellence.
